The evidence with the title 'Women are still paid less than men - even in the same job ' says Mar 31, 2016  ... That women receive lower wages than men is a known fact of most economies .  ... That is , women are earning less for the same work .  ... Market , it is commonly thought , may lower the average for their entire gender.  ... The first place this starts is paying women the same wages as men for doing similarwork . 
